This led them to do without, in the first place, the automatic roof which was replaced by a manual sheeted roof, allowing to reduce by 21 kilos, to use aluminum doors like those of the GT3, 15 other kilos less, to remove the air conditioner, 13 kilos, to reduce the fuel tank from 64 to 54 liters, 7 kilos of gained, to mount sports bins, still 12 kilos, and with light tires of 19 inches.
