This estimation and sales service is aimed exclusively at professionals in the sector, such as insurance companies, experts, rental companies, garages, scrapyards and professional sellers who must be registered before starting to carry out operations.
This platform was created in 1996 in Germany and manages more than 650,000 operations throughout Europe, including 500,000 in Germany.
Among its main markets are Spain, Greece, Poland and Turkey.
There are currently more than 1500 sellers and 4000 experts registered on the site.
